Run the following in claude ai

Create SKILL.md file for python text processor
Should be a multi turn API conversations. 
Keep full conversation history and send to Claude as part of API requests (most recent 20)
First ask the user to enter the text input to be analyzed and End the text input with pressing Ctrl+D on Mac/Linux.
Then ask the user what to do with input text / instruction eg. summarize key points, shorten text, make it more formal, etc. Enf the instruction by pressing Ctrl+D on Mac/Linux.
Then ask the user if output is OK or do more.
Repeat.
If the user enters "quit", then end the program execution. 
API keys should be in .env. 
Use APIError and RateLimitError for stable API responses
At the end of program execution,output shold be dumped into a JSON file
Use System prompt and ensure the text processor as friendly AI assistant
(1) Ensure output is valid json format, focused and not too long
(2) Ask clarifying questions if needed before generating output
(3) if the user is stuck, guide them and motivate them to ask the right question, do not guess


